Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:09.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:09.99,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,My dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,First Year, Peach Class, Ayasaki Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:25.77,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,My father and mother are always being bums at home, regardless of it being weekday or weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Father is searching for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:32.74,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Mother is into finding a way to beat the slot machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:37.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Father says he'll take me to Hawaii if he wins the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:44.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But Mother says "We can't get passports, so that's impossible" and laughs, so my house is always filled with laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:46.69,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And my dream is to...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:58.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of what I was told yesterday at Milady's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:06.42,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words, your life is infinitely worthless, I take it. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:10.28,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, come on! Keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.11,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I made up my mind, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:17.02,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the meaning in my life, but right now, I'll protect Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:22.53,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:26.00,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who dedicates himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:31.87,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian who supports the days of their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:41.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is a super combat battle story of a boy who fights, risking his life for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:44.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Ayasaki Hayate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll do my best today, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.48,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What? My dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:35.36,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,If I were pressed, there's one person whose future I'm really worried about, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:39.75,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,so I would have to say my dream is for her to become a fine adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.09,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But why ask this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, how do I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:50.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams are like the motivation for people to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.58,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:58.02,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, if you apply that theory,\Nmy motivation to live is a little iffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:04.69,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto Ryouma said that we should have a dream\Nas large as the Pacific, since we are born as humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:09.28,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And Mozart said that life has meaning because there are dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:15.04,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A spy from England said that a person who can't come up with a huge dream must have a life worthless like trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:18.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.47,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just going through a minor depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:25.26,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But still, Hayate-kun, you seem a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:28.98,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Did Nagi's grandfather say something to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:32.88,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's like the idea of always remembering the mindset of a novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:38.30,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm going to do my best as the butler Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.09,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:51.97,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get a wink of sleep because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:59.91,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you from anyone who tries to make you cry. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.64,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right with you? {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:09.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate is so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.22,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun's working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.25,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,He said something about the novice mind and a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.43,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:27.87,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,He's working really hard,\Nlike a businessman who has found meaning in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:32.81,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be for the future between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.72,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think you have it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:39.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.39,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually it's fine, but I'm not mentally prepared yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:45.96,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how about you? Do you have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.73,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Wouldn't anyone have a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:53.66,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Like I want to be a manga author\Nand sell 100 billion copies of what I publish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:54.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.94,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. You're too dazzling for me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:02.04,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But what exactly could Hayate's dream be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:07.67,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but since he made such a big speech,\NI'm sure he has something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:14.92,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But Nagi, I'm sure the dream you have in mind is different from what he has in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.69,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,On another note, what could Hayate-kun's dream really be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.96,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What? My dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:23.77,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:30.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But that was like a kid's mistake, and it's embarrassing to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.47,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry, I won't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.49,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,3LDK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:46.05,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Note: 3LDK is a Japanese housing term which stands for\N"3 individual rooms, Living room, Dining room, and Kitchen"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.05,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,3LDK!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:57.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsc90}And my dream is to live in an apartment with 3 separate rooms\Nwith a living room, dining room, and a kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:02.00,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a 3LDK peacefully without being chased by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason is-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.93,Default-alt,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Tha... That's enough. You can stop now Ayasaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:11.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see. So your dream is to live in a 3LDK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is that too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.65,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.24,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the dream, the better...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.18,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:31.10,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that your cell phone is still broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.55,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's inconvenient,\Nso please go buy another one with your budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, then right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:42.15,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you need to take some breaks once in a while,\Nso you can have the day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.53,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,So how about strolling around the city a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.91,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a good one since I had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.38,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what the One-Seg function is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.32,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I can have a TV-Phone with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:58.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I can store 1,000 email addresses. This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't need that many.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have that many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.10,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wonder what my friends in high school are doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.74,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,School, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:12.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had a chance to go,\Nso I haven't dealt with it all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:16.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I did pay the entire tuition, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking? Could I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.22,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,...want to return to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:35.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I came on a whim, but it's hard to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:38.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But I should still be a student of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I have to not act suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:40.52,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.03,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a suspicious person, at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.50,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,You're Hayate-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Nishizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:51.33,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's been since Christmas when we last met.\NWhat have you been doing up till now? {ep 11} {Dei- reworded a bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.70,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:57.19,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Souya-kun and the rest were all worried about you, too,\Nsince you never come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:09:00.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot has happened since the end of last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.39,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,A lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:04.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:08.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, there's a huge debt, and my parents disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:13.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,and I was given to very generous people as a present because of the debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.34,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:23.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot has happened,\Nand I'm working as a butler at a certain mansion. {ep 11}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:29.42,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it's a joke? You're such a kidder, Hayate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:34.50,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm really glad. I'm finally able to see your face this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.69,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:40.68,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing. Don't take my words so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing flirting by the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.00,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,S-Souya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it you quit school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really quit it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad, Nishizawa, to have your dear Prince back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.12,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:02.39,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot or something, Souya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.35,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural to worry about classmates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:09.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But you were about to cry when you heard he'd quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.54,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So you were worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Nishizawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:16.96,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course, since we're classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe I should try and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.56,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.10,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You've dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.71,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for the teacher to say such a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.61,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Nishizawa. I'm only speaking the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:38.68,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki's parents came here around noon on Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:42.68,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,...and told us to give them back\Nthe remaining tuition since he would no longer come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:48.91,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun, weren't you paying your own tuition\Nsince your parents wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.31,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:53.27,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's harsh for you to consider him dropped out\Nbecause you gave his parents the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:56.69,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,But they said to give the money, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:57.84,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so I can't go to school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.96,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Hayate-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.41,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to disappear like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:07.13,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:10.32,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,If we bring this up\Nbefore the board of education, then I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:17.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, the teachers will have to take responsibility for my parents' selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:26.13,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is goodbye, Nishizawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:32.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It was only for a short time, but goodbye, my high school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.74,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.48,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.25,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say goodbye like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.79,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,So please go out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The moment she said that, I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:01.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Without thinking, her face spontaneously came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:11.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Her sad face hit me hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.19,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Will you date me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:15.99,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:17.82,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.79,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.78,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,...only interested in 2-D girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.26,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Gahhh!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Actually right now, I have someone I can't leave untended.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.77,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To Hayate who's not used to girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:44.06,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,he thought it'd be more manly to reject her\Nso she would come to hate him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:48.12,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but comedy anime main characters never get dumped with dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I've just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.12,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,A minor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:12:59.15,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you bought a cell phone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.43,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.85,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to it, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:05.75,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:10.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I registered my address in the number 1 slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.28,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Call or email me as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:22.65,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:26.93,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun, I haven't given up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.95,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you pay, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.89,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo daifuku
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.89,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo daifuku = Bean paste with strawberry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.86,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Kuru kuru mawaru yume nante...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.86,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Kuru kuru mawaru yume nante... = Dreams of spinning drums are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.22,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Here Wataru-kun, I finished these, so I brought them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.45,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,So how were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.75,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,60%, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:51.15,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I told you they're not movies girls can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:54.34,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm at an age that I want to understand guys' minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.26,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,You learn about guys' minds from monster movies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:14:01.49,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,But Nishizawa-san, the boy you like quit school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:05.72,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! His house was empty and there wasn't any hint of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.53,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to meet him at least one more time and talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.50,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find a lost person like that, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.40,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say such a hopeless thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.15,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Wataru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:23.68,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I don't usually watch them, but are animes interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:29.39,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Only the ones I thought were interesting are on those shelves, but I don't know if you'd find them interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.25,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Stop those "ehh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:35.03,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Interesting or uninteresting is only a personal opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:37.96,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find out until you watch and check them out yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.65,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,So stop whining and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.60,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Think, then act.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:46.11,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Think if it will be really interesting for you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.90,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's my coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:52.15,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,But since they're all rented out, start with Getsumen To Heiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:57.01,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you bamboo vendor! Always getting in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.64,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just remembered something I need to do, so I'll head home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:56.99,Default-alt,Car,0000,0000,0000,,Bamboo... Bamboo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:00.41,Default-alt,Car,0000,0000,0000,,Bamboo... Bamboo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.48,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, she got away.	
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:05.17,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take better care of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:09.65,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,But can you really find someone who's disappeared in this huge city?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.36,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been a really nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.86,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru-kun, we finished these, so I'm here to return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.08,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey debt-ridden butler. How were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:24.00,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a good life lesson from them, but Milady didn't like them much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.81,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The two never manage to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:27.89,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:28.97,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.36,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki asked for me to get a tape, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.43,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,No way, is that Hayate-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.24,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to meet at a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.02,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Are we destined to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:45.41,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time to me to lose myself in a delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:46.39,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.02,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun! Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.73,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.07,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:01.01,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,He's so fast. I can't catch up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:04.54,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I have to keep up so I don't lose sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.91,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,He finally finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.65,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,So could he be living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.55,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.65,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait? It's more like a mansion than a house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.19,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Hayate-kun living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:23.13,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Hayate-kun said something about being in debt or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:27.16,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Then this must be a yaku** house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.33,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun must be going through lots of troubles in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:36.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Can we hear your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.01,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What? A suspicious girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:43.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it might be one of Milady's friends, so we wanted to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.47,Default-alt,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.36,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Black suits and scary faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.73,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely yaku**!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.44,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:55.16,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be treated to activities\Nthat can't be made viewable for young audiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.62,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Public school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.43,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's from Hayate-kun's old school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:06.06,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't look like she's someone suspicious,\Nso please let her hands go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:06.19,Default-alt,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:06.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let her hands go for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:09.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:12.24,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:15.72,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I didn't say let her get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry; we'll catch her right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:30.80,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to get away, but I have no clue where Hayate-kun is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.14,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, yaku** people are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:39.18,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Wataru-kun won't believe me\Nif I tell him a mansion this big exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.94,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I have to find Hayate-kun fast and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.01,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Comedic shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.02,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Realistic shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.25,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:56.05,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a tiger at a house in Japan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.87,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really die from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.93,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,And it's chasing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.93,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I chasing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:05.36,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my hunting instinct I thought I had lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.15,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:09.33,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall listen to my instinct and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.10,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,...I shall...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.19,Default,Tam,0000,0000,0000,,Lick her all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.61,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's the wrong instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.01,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:23.41,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ina**ma Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.97,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ina**ma Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:31.03,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's an ultimate move for only those who have overcome hardship with effort and guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I never trained, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:40.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,God... He's causing trouble as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:46.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to the DVDs we rented from Wataru-kun, I shouted out the attack name, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what I meant by a life lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.40,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.60,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Nishizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.45,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:57.70,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.93,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.37,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.27,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:11.23,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,There are things you can tell the moment you lay eyes upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.80,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, who is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.80,0:19:17.44,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's Nishizawa-san. My former classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.34,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun, and she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:24.01,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She's Lady Nagi, this mansion's-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.78,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It's women's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:37.09,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The people who are destined to fight over someone dear to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.20,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The moment they saw each other, they both knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.96,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They are rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.83,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,What? My background is a hamster?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.23,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,It got eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.75,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,My hamster's weak, so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:07.94,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll step aside for today,\Nbut I'll bring a stronger hamster next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:09.71,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured and wait for me, Hayate-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Nishizawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.00,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She's a funny person, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.34,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:24.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You can't leave me and go somewhere else, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:32.58,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry. I don't have\Nanywhere to go other than here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:55.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Because there are those who can't even if they want to. {ep9}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:18.97,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:20.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:25.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate has done a lot for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.03,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I must answer his kindness as his master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:31.88,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Nagi has made up some kind of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll fight against the huge school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.16,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And leaving that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.19,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,For today, I'll borrow these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.69,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.67,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Business, business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.62,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Kendama and Carrot is rented out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:49.54,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they just got rented.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:50.59,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Andarta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:52.69,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru's video shop is making business.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:54.79,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They're having 50%-off service, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:31.46,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:32.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:33.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Ayasaki Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:37.82,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sanzenin Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:41.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, the BGM will be Milady's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:46.03,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The ability to sing is an important factor as the next head of Sanzenin family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:49.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It describes well how rough and hard to tame you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:51.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What, is that supposed to be a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.24,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:57.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You can sense your charming acts from the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.49,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Charming? You make me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:23:59.78,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:03.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, some paperwork has arrived from Hakuou Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.18,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's a transfer form.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:05.76,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:06.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:08.72,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean mine?!
